OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBanksy writes tribute to   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcomedian Tony Allen        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Banksy has penned a rare statement to  
OL,6, remember late comedian and "born       
OL,7, troublemaker" Tony Allen.              
OL,9,FThe secretive artist normally lets his 
OL,10,Fpictures do the talking but wrote his  
OL,11,Ftribute to Allen for BBC Radio 4       
OL,12,Fobituary programme Last Word.          
OL,14,FAllen, one of the founders of the      
OL,15,Falternative comedy movement in the     
OL,16,F1970s, died at the start of December.  
OL,18,FBanksy enlisted him to train the surly 
OL,19,Fstewards at his dystopian theme park in
OL,20,FWeston-super-Mare in 2015.             
